    <h2>Privacy Policy & Cookies</h2>
    
    <p>At Roberts International Airport, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This page explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you visit our website.</p>

    <h3>1. Data We Collect</h3>
    <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Personal details (e.g., name, email, contact information) provided during bookings or registration.</li>
        <li>Cookies and tracking data (e.g., IP address, browser type, page interactions).</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>2. Use of Your Data</h3>
    <p>Your data is used to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Process bookings and provide flight status updates.</li>
        <li>Enhance the user experience through personalized content.</li>
        <li>Analyze site traffic and improve website performance.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. Cookies Policy</h3>
    <p>We use cookies to improve your browsing experience. You can manage your cookie preferences or disable them in your browser settings.</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Essential Cookies</strong>: Necessary for website functionality.</li>
        <li><strong>Analytics Cookies</strong>: Help us understand how you use our website.</li>
        <li><strong>Advertising Cookies</strong>: Used to show personalized ads.</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>4. Sharing Your Data</h3>
    <p>We may share your data with trusted third-party partners, such as airlines and hotel booking services, to enhance your experience. We also share data with analytics providers to improve website functionality.</p>

    <h3>5. Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access and request copies of your personal information.</li>
        <li>Request that we correct or delete your data.</li>
        <li>Opt out of cookies or marketing communications.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>6. Security</h3>
    <p>We use industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access.</p>

    <h3>7. Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have any questions about our Privacy and Cookies Policy, please contact us at privacy@robertsairport.com.</p>

    <h3>8. Policy Updates</h3>
    <p>We regularly review and update this policy. Significant changes will be communicated via email or a prominent notice on our website.</p>
